in your life.

36
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:02,160
No wonder he acted weird today.

37
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:05,280
Is he going to ask me
for compensation again?

38
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:09,920
How should I face him in the future?

39
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,360
Hello?

40
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:18,760
Ye Ran.

41
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:21,640
Tomorrow is the Saturday we agreed on.

42
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,160
Are you bringing your boyfriend for lunch

43
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,240
or dinner?

44
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,680
Tomorrow

45
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,120
