51
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,440
Shall we change the day then?

52
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,280
I've made it clear.

53
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:44,080
This is your last chance.

54
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:46,920
Understood.

55
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,800
I promise
you'll meet your future son-in-law.

56
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:03,160
Boyfriend...

57
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,160
Am I going crazy?

58
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:12,080
I can't possibly bring Tiger Meng.

59
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,160
I'll ask Chen Zhuangzhuang instead.

60
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,160
Even if we broke up,

61
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,840
he should do me this favor.

62
00:03:19,780 --> 00:03:20,620
I'll help him

63
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,800
pursue Ye Dang if needed.

64
00:03:25,020 --> 00:03:26,900
(Silence)

65
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:28,400
Zhuangzhuang, are you asleep?

66
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,560
I need a favor.

67
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,240
Why isn't he

68
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,560
