69
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,640
Could he be bailing on me?

70
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,360
Ye Dang, it's urgent.

71
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,360
Do you know anyone

72
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,400
who could play my boyfriend?

73
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,520
I asked Secretary Chen,

74
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,240
but he hasn't shown up yet.

75
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,200
I'm near our place.

76
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,840
Please help me out.

77
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,520
Mr. Meng,

78
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,800
what brings you here?

79
00:04:17,520 --> 00:04:18,560
I heard someone

80
00:04:18,840 --> 00:04:20,440
urgently needs a boyfriend.

81
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,640
Look.

82
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,680
How about me?

83
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,520
No.

84
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,480
Why not?

85
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,760
You already exceed
the standards in appearance,

86
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,080
and you're well-dressed

87
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,360
with a nice car.

88
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,440
So,

89
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,440
what's the problem?

90
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,240
I told my mom

91
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,040
my boyfriend is a secretary,

92
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,920
average-looking

93
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,720
with normal conditions.

94
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,280
You don't seem like that.

95
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:54,280
Mr. Meng,

96
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,280
are you really here to help me?

97
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:57,920
Why else would I be here?

98
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,880
(Is he here to retaliate)

99
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,680
(for that night?)

100
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,400
(Did she remember something?)

101
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,280
So,

102
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:09,720
what should we do now?

103
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,120
(Forget it.)

104
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:15,000
(I'll just make the best
of a bad situation.)

105
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,440
Come with me.

106
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,240
What do you want from me?

107
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:52,920
Ye Dang,

108
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,160
Ye Ran and I have talked things out.

109
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,040
I want to pursue you.

110
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,800
I don't need a boyfriend.

111
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,560
Then can we start as friends?

112
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,680
Just ordinary friends.

113
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,760
I don't need a boyfriend,

114
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,400
but I do need a client.

115
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,360
How about becoming a member?

116
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,120
I'll give you a decent discount.

117
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,320
It's quite a good deal now.

118
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:21,340
(Chen)

119
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,560
When can we start training?

120
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:28,760
Anytime.

121
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,520
You can take your time.

122
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,600
I'll leave first.

123
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,920
Aren't you supposed to teach me?

124
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:44,600
