126
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,400
I can pay more.

127
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,320
It's urgent.

128
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,360
Do you know anyone

129
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:55,440
who could play my boyfriend?

130
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,200
I asked Secretary Chen,

131
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,880
but he hasn't shown up yet.

132
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,840
He dared to

133
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,600
blow Ye Ran off again.

134
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,920
Is it okay now?

135
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,920
You still don't look ordinary enough.

136
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,160
If only I could cover this face
with something.

137
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:46,160
Oh, don't forget,

138
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,360
today you're playing

139
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,480
the most ordinary working-class guy.

140
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,240
Don't blow your cover.

141
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,400
Hello, ma'am.

142
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,880
I'm Ye Ran's boyfriend.

143
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,440
Chen Zhuangzhuang, right?

144
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,520
Yes.

145
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,360
He's had an allergic reaction
on his face,

146
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,640
