147
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,560
So he can't take off his mask.

148
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,520
It doesn't matter.

149
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,960
There's nothing to see anyway.

150
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,080
Have some tea.

151
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,520
Thank you, ma'am.

152
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,040
Well...

153
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,800
