156
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,960
Yes,

157
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,280
I've just paid the down payment.

158
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:50,880
It's a three-bedroom, two-bathroom place.

159
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,440
Do you have a car?

160
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,920
I have a used car,

161
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,120
but I don't drive it much.

162
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,760
People like us in the working class

163
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,800
