164
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,560
What about

165
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:04,280
your plans and goals in life?

166
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:05,880
Just the two of us,

167
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,500
three meals a day,

168
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:08,600
spending all four seasons together.

169
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:11,800
I just want to live a simple

170
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:13,520
and happy life

171
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:15,320
