are you planning to have?

175
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:27,240
We still have a mortgage to pay off.

176
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:28,640
No rush.

177
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:30,120
It's up to Ye Ran.

178
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,880
That does sound pretty ordinary.

179
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:34,760
Hello?

180
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:36,880
Who is it?

181
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,160
Coming, coming.

182
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:49,320
Hello, ma'am. Is this Ye Ran's house?

183
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,760
Yes, you are?

184
00:09:50,830 --> 00:09:51,950
I'm Ye Ran's boyfriend.

